To run php on your computer we need to Follow the few steps:


1). Downloading and installing xampp
2). Downloading and installing Vscode


now after doing the installtion part we need to do simple things.

1). open your xampp Folder . go to htdocs and create a new folder.
2). open open that folder in vs code.
3). Start your xampp server.


Writing our first program in php

1) Now go to vscode where you have opened a folder
2). Create a new file - index.php

3).  code-

<?php


echo "Hello world";

>?


4). Now open your file in the browser :
   http://localhost/YOUR_FOLDER_NAME/
   
5). And congratulations You have successfully installed PHP.
